{"tid":2197891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【強国】珠海酒店大爆炸 現場多名傷者 多間商店損毁","createTime":"2020-09-11T03:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T04:05:08.000Z","uid":134908,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"616d008734901b57e516f615e64df61f96e55b5c","tid":2197891,"uid":134908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wFLVEGA3dTYyz1_VXdLU64ubbx0=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GM4YVYHTUNEGTMLQ7FYQNCJTOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwFLVEGA3dTYyz1_VXdLU64ubbx0%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGM4YVYHTUNEGTMLQ7FYQNCJTOM.jpg&h=6b07a2c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東珠海市斗門區白藤頭騰湖大酒店，今日9時許發生爆炸。酒店一處窗戶疑因起火冒出大量濃煙，當時街上有不少市民圍觀，隨後突然發生爆炸，火焰從窗戶拼發而出，玻璃碎散落街道，圍觀市民隨即爭相走避，街上商店炸得一片頹垣敗瓦。當地消防部門出動4個中隊、11輛消防車以及55名消防員到場救援，目前已經救出多名傷者，搜救還在持續，暫時至少救出3名傷者。<br />\n<br />\n有網民指，現場有二次爆炸，「然後吃瓜群眾部份受傷」，亦有指附近有一所少兒藝術中心以及幼兒園，未知是否也受波及。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fpzA4CZvsXizGSW_7IAdFkz4oLk=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BSAWN7TWNFHBLMQ5BG6GKKAUHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfpzA4CZvsXizGSW_7IAdFkz4oLk%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBSAWN7TWNFHBLMQ5BG6GKKAUHE.jpg&h=ee97a200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AQLbR2HNbQMBJUi4i2BGm_e_lhQ=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P6TZGRLPCZDVXLT6IZF4HYIAU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAQLbR2HNbQMBJUi4i2BGm_e_lhQ%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2